### Supplier Management ###

### Get all suppliers (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/suppliers?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get supplier by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/suppliers/{{id}}
Accept: application/json

### Create new supplier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Tech Supplies Inc.",
  "contactPerson": "John Smith",
  "phone": "+1-555-123-4567",
  "email": "contact@techsupplies.com",
  "address": "123 Tech Street, Suite 456",
  "city": "San Francisco",
  "state": "California",
  "zipCode": "94105",
  "country": "United States",
  "notes": "Preferred supplier for electronic components",
  "isActive": true
}

### Update supplier
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/suppliers/{{id}}
